    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Chakra Control </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 10 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 23</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You focus Chakra into a part of your body, which you use to strike the ground below you to create a powerful shockwave. Any creature finding itself underground and within 30 ft of the surface is thrown upwards 1d6 x 5 ft and takes 2d6 bludgeoning damage. Creatures standing on the ground are instead knocked prone (Reflex negates). You are unaffected by this technique.</p>\n\n\n\n",
